- Believe me, you don't
wanna go down that road.

1:10:45.241 --> 1:10:47.243
- [Suzy] Pretty rough, huh?

1:10:49.897 --> 1:10:54.728
- Yeah, I was pulled from the
street against my will and...

1:10:57.862 --> 1:11:00.604
- Bruce, how did
it happen, I mean,

1:11:00.691 --> 1:11:05.261
I saw you at church, we said
goodbye and that was it.

1:11:05.348 --> 1:11:08.786
Do you feel like
talking about it?

1:11:08.873 --> 1:11:12.224
- Well, let's just say
I didn't get very far.

1:11:12.311 --> 1:11:15.183
Maybe a couple
blocks, that was it.

1:11:15.271 --> 1:11:17.098
A car pulled up and,

1:11:19.275 --> 1:11:20.058
Tiberius,

1:11:21.494 --> 1:11:22.321
the leader,

1:11:23.453 --> 1:11:24.454
he was there.

1:11:26.020 --> 1:11:28.719
And he asked me for
directions to Herb's Garage.

1:11:28.806 --> 1:11:30.416
- Yeah, I remember that place.

1:11:30.503 --> 1:11:34.725
- Yeah, we all did, and so
I didn't expect a thing.

1:11:36.857 --> 1:11:38.685
I walked right into it.

1:11:41.166 --> 1:11:43.342
He flashed a gun
and pulled me in

1:11:43.429 --> 1:11:48.216
and that night they showed
me what they wanted with me.

1:11:48.304 --> 1:11:50.871
Made me make my
first drop and...

1:11:52.177 --> 1:11:54.397
The things they made me do.

1:11:58.183 --> 1:11:59.619
Unspeakable things.

1:12:01.273 --> 1:12:05.408
And maybe I didn't have a
choice, at the beginning.

1:12:05.495 --> 1:12:06.278
Later on?

1:12:08.933 --> 1:12:10.978
I'm not so sure.

1:12:11.065 --> 1:12:14.765
- Brucie, you don't have to
be a product of your past.

1:12:14.852 --> 1:12:16.157
[Brucie laughs]

1:12:16.244 --> 1:12:17.507
- That's quite the
sentiment you have there.

1:12:17.594 --> 1:12:19.117
You'd have better
luck selling that

1:12:19.204 --> 1:12:23.556
to the greeting card
company than you would me.

1:12:23.643 --> 1:12:26.124
- Actually, I've been
down this rough road

1:12:26.211 --> 1:12:28.996
with other people and
I've seen them get free

1:12:29.083 --> 1:12:32.348
from their past and find
a hope then a future.

1:12:32.435 --> 1:12:33.827
It doesn't happen overnight,
but with some help--

1:12:33.914 --> 1:12:35.307
- And what?

1:12:35.394 --> 1:12:39.093
And you wanna make me
one of your pet projects?

1:12:40.094 --> 1:12:41.357
I don't think so.

1:12:42.880 --> 1:12:45.099
- Okay, I'm not
saying that your life

1:12:45.186 --> 1:12:48.146
has to be like a greeting card.

1:12:48.233 --> 1:12:52.803
Very few are, but you
don't have to let your past

1:12:52.890 --> 1:12:54.848
dictate your future
or who you are.

1:12:54.935 --> 1:12:57.590
- Nature versus nurture would
argue with that one, too.

1:12:57.677 --> 1:12:58.939
Wouldn't it?

1:12:59.026 --> 1:13:00.245
- Still smart as
ever, aren't you?

1:13:00.332 --> 1:13:02.552
- Hey, who you talkin' to?

1:13:02.639 --> 1:13:04.118
- Yeah, I know.

1:13:04.205 --> 1:13:08.601
Look, you can bring psychology
or science into this,

1:13:08.688 --> 1:13:12.605
but I still know you and aside
from whatever they made you

1:13:12.692 --> 1:13:16.174
do or whoever they tried
to make you become,

1:13:16.261 --> 1:13:17.784
that's not who you are.

1:13:19.395 --> 1:13:21.962
There's so much more
for your life, Brucie,

1:13:22.049 --> 1:13:23.616
and I know that with God--

1:13:23.703 --> 1:13:26.227
- Enough with the
intervention, okay?

1:13:26.314 --> 1:13:28.229
I've been down that road.

1:13:28.316 --> 1:13:30.275
Twice I gave God a chance,

1:13:31.407 --> 1:13:33.365
and it didn't go anywhere.

1:13:37.282 --> 1:13:40.807
- Well, I better see
if I can find Alicia.

1:13:40.894 --> 1:13:42.505
You gonna be around?

1:13:42.592 --> 1:13:43.375
- Yeah.

1:13:46.509 --> 1:13:49.337
I have some unfinished business.

1:14:01.915 --> 1:14:03.439
- It's good to see you
this evening, Bruce.

1:14:03.526 --> 1:14:05.397
- You too, Candy.

1:14:05.484 --> 1:14:08.400
[moody rock music]

1:14:13.492 --> 1:14:14.275
- 180 in!

1:14:18.323 --> 1:14:19.585
- Good evening, sir.

1:14:19.672 --> 1:14:21.369
Thank you for being here.

1:14:21.457 --> 1:14:22.458
- Thank you.

1:14:37.821 --> 1:14:42.478
♪ Comes on like a lamb
but then she's a lion ♪

1:14:44.088 --> 1:14:47.918
♪ My baby's love
needs no denyin' ♪

1:14:49.528 --> 1:14:52.836
♪ She knows exactly
just what to do ♪

1:14:54.490 --> 1:14:58.276
♪ My baby's love make
me feel brand new ♪

1:14:59.973 --> 1:15:03.324
♪ Oh, she's electric,
she lights my fuse ♪

1:15:04.978 --> 1:15:09.287
♪ She's hot-wired,
got nothin' to lose ♪

1:15:10.984 --> 1:15:15.032
♪ Don't you wanna know
what my baby does ♪

1:15:15.119 --> 1:15:19.645
♪ My baby moves me
with spark plug love ♪

1:15:21.429 --> 1:15:24.911
♪ My baby grooves me
with spark plug love ♪

1:15:26.652 --> 1:15:30.351
♪ My baby chills me
with spark plug love ♪

1:15:32.092 --> 1:15:35.922
♪ My baby thrills me
with spark plug love ♪

1:15:37.533 --> 1:15:39.535
♪ Spark plug love,
spark plug love ♪

1:15:39.622 --> 1:15:40.274
- Yes!

1:15:40.361 --> 1:15:41.972
Woo!

1:15:42.059 --> 1:15:45.671
♪ My baby thrills me
with spark plug love ♪

1:15:45.758 --> 1:15:48.544
♪ Yes, she does ♪

1:16:08.433 --> 1:16:11.479
[dark orchestral music]

1:16:11.567 --> 1:16:13.438
[thud]

1:16:57.264 --> 1:16:59.702
[Brucie yells]

1:17:05.055 --> 1:17:07.623
[Brucie sobs]

1:17:36.042 --> 1:17:36.782
- Hello.

1:17:37.914 --> 1:17:38.654
I'm Gabe.

1:17:39.655 --> 1:17:40.917
- [Brucie] Yeah?

1:17:41.004 --> 1:17:41.744
So?

1:17:43.746 --> 1:17:47.488
- [Gabe] Would you like
to make a small wager?

1:17:47.575 --> 1:17:50.535
- I don't have
anything left to wager.

1:17:50.622 --> 1:17:52.580
- [Gabe] Oh, but you do.

1:17:54.278 --> 1:17:58.804
If you lose, you'll see all
the things you've ever done.

1:18:01.546 --> 1:18:05.463
- I lived through
everything I've done.

1:18:05.550 --> 1:18:09.510
I don't figure where
seeing it again would hurt.

1:18:11.295 --> 1:18:12.905
What do I get if I win?

1:18:12.992 --> 1:18:14.341
[Gabe chuckles]

1:18:14.428 --> 1:18:15.603
- Untold riches.

1:18:21.392 --> 1:18:24.351
[suspenseful music]

1:18:28.573 --> 1:18:29.705
- Let's do this.

1:18:34.535 --> 1:18:36.450
- A cut of the cards.

1:18:36.537 --> 1:18:37.582
Takes all.

1:18:39.540 --> 1:18:40.324
Agreed?

1:18:41.978 --> 1:18:42.718
- Agreed.

1:18:46.722 --> 1:18:49.028
- [Gabe] Would you
like to go first?

1:18:49.115 --> 1:18:49.855
- No.

1:18:50.726 --> 1:18:51.857
No.

1:18:51.944 --> 1:18:54.207
- Very well, I'll go first.

1:19:08.526 --> 1:19:09.745
Are you ready?

1:19:15.359 --> 1:19:17.883
[ominous tones]

1:19:21.495 --> 1:19:23.759
[rumbling]

1:19:26.370 --> 1:19:28.198
[Water drips]

1:19:28.285 --> 1:19:30.809
[static hisses]

1:19:49.915 --> 1:19:51.917
- There was another
shooting down on Livingston.

1:19:52.004 --> 1:19:54.572
- It seem like shots
happen all the time now.

1:19:54.659 --> 1:19:56.617
Sometimes it even
keeps me up at night.

1:19:56.704 --> 1:19:58.576
I gotta get out of this place.

1:19:58.663 --> 1:20:01.622
- Yeah, me too, I'm
not too far from there.

1:20:01.709 --> 1:20:03.363
Anyway, be careful out there.

1:20:03.450 --> 1:20:05.888
- Thank you, have a good night.

1:20:08.804 --> 1:20:11.154
[door creaks]

1:20:11.241 --> 1:20:15.071
[suspenseful orchestral music]

1:20:28.432 --> 1:20:30.782
- Give me your money!
- Okay, okay, okay.

1:20:30.869 --> 1:20:32.349
[sobs]

1:20:32.436 --> 1:20:33.916
- Give me your money
or I'll kill ya!

1:20:34.003 --> 1:20:35.439
- I don't wanna die,
please don't kill me!

1:20:35.526 --> 1:20:38.181
- Give me your money!
- Okay, okay, okay.

1:20:38.268 --> 1:20:39.660
[sobs]

1:20:39.747 --> 1:20:42.489
[thud]

1:20:42.576 --> 1:20:45.710
[paper rustles]

1:20:45.797 --> 1:20:48.669
[door creaks]

1:20:48.756 --> 1:20:51.281
[engine starts]

1:21:25.706 --> 1:21:27.883
[knocks]

1:21:27.970 --> 1:21:30.886
[glass shatters]

1:22:13.841 --> 1:22:16.670
- I wanna talk to you
all about choices today.

1:22:16.757 --> 1:22:18.455
Already since you
woke up this morning,

1:22:18.542 --> 1:22:20.631
you have made a lot of choices.

1:22:20.718 --> 1:22:23.373
You made the choice to
be here today, right?

1:22:23.460 --> 1:22:27.768
And so, choices are a big
part of everything that we do.

1:22:27.855 --> 1:22:31.947
I want you to think about the
choice that the Father made

1:22:32.034 --> 1:22:35.080
for you and I to send the son,
Jesus Christ, to die for us.

1:22:35.167 --> 1:22:37.039
- What am I doing here?

1:22:38.910 --> 1:22:41.913
Besides, what has
God done for me?

1:22:44.046 --> 1:22:47.658
- [Speaker] Shedding
his blood for you and I.

1:22:54.186 --> 1:22:57.363
[Brucie cries]

1:22:57.450 --> 1:22:59.975
[mother cries]

1:23:01.802 --> 1:23:02.890
- Oh, no, no!

1:23:04.936 --> 1:23:07.069
Don't you give her that baby.

1:23:07.156 --> 1:23:09.941
Why you looking at me like that?

1:23:10.028 --> 1:23:13.814
I told you we can't afford
another mouth to feed!

1:23:13.901 --> 1:23:15.860
Give it to me, I'll
take care of it.

1:23:15.947 --> 1:23:18.819
I'll dispose of it
just like I said.

1:23:18.906 --> 1:23:20.996
- I'll take care of it.

1:23:22.823 --> 1:23:24.869
- You can't even get out of bed!

1:23:24.956 --> 1:23:26.610
[mother sobs]

1:23:26.697 --> 1:23:28.003
"Take care of it."

1:23:32.311 --> 1:23:33.573
- Get out!

1:23:33.660 --> 1:23:34.922
[sobs]

1:23:35.010 --> 1:23:37.186
Go get your dope!

1:23:37.273 --> 1:23:38.665
Go get your fix!

1:23:41.494 --> 1:23:43.366
[sobs]

1:23:44.628 --> 1:23:47.979
[somber orchestral music]

1:23:51.504 --> 1:23:53.376
[sobs]

1:24:05.823 --> 1:24:07.868
- [chuckles] Hey, let's
just get this money

1:24:07.955 --> 1:24:10.523
and get outta here real quick.

1:24:14.005 --> 1:24:16.268
Hey, what up, Brucie?

1:24:16.355 --> 1:24:17.878
- What's up, Bruce?

1:24:17.965 --> 1:24:19.880
- I got that for you.

1:24:21.360 --> 1:24:24.233
You didn't get that from me.

1:24:24.320 --> 1:24:25.843
- You didn't see us.

1:24:25.930 --> 1:24:27.758
- Have a good night.

1:24:43.904 --> 1:24:46.820
[train horn blows]

1:24:55.002 --> 1:24:57.440
[Brucie sighs]

1:25:26.425 --> 1:25:27.252
[rumbling]

1:25:27.339 --> 1:25:30.081
[Brucie gasps]

1:25:50.493 --> 1:25:52.886
[guns bang]

1:25:57.761 --> 1:25:58.936
- Don't shoot, man.

1:25:59.023 --> 1:26:00.285
- Shut up!
- I'm not with them!

1:26:00.372 --> 1:26:03.158
- God, I wanna shoot you so bad.

1:26:12.471 --> 1:26:16.127
[homeless man laughs wildly]

1:26:21.176 --> 1:26:22.916
- Where ya going?

1:26:23.003 --> 1:26:25.180
[giggles]

1:26:31.186 --> 1:26:33.057
- You're lucky the hit
was for Tiberius, John,

1:26:33.144 --> 1:26:34.667
and his goons outside.

1:26:34.754 --> 1:26:36.191
I suggest you get out of town,

1:26:36.278 --> 1:26:39.106
and never let me see
you again, you got me?

1:26:39.194 --> 1:26:41.544
- [Hit Man] Let's go, come on!

1:27:36.033 --> 1:27:38.383
[door creaks]

1:27:40.429 --> 1:27:42.953
[wind howls]

1:27:48.088 --> 1:27:49.220
- I'm sorry.

1:27:49.307 --> 1:27:50.743
I'm sorry, God.

1:27:50.830 --> 1:27:52.745
I'm sorry, forgive me.

1:27:52.832 --> 1:27:54.225
Forgive me, God.

1:27:55.313 --> 1:27:56.227
Forgive me.

1:27:59.317 --> 1:28:00.100
The deuce.

1:28:01.319 --> 1:28:03.930
[melancholy piano music]

1:28:04.017 --> 1:28:07.543
It was the two times I
walked away from you.

1:28:08.935 --> 1:28:10.633
- Everyone back up, please.

1:28:10.720 --> 1:28:12.548
Back up, go about your business.

1:28:12.635 --> 1:28:14.201
Get out of here.

1:28:14.289 --> 1:28:15.246
Excuse me, sir?

1:28:15.333 --> 1:28:16.552
You all right?

1:28:23.950 --> 1:28:25.082
You're Bruce.

1:28:27.563 --> 1:28:28.303
- Yeah.

1:28:31.044 --> 1:28:32.568
But how do you know?

1:28:35.353 --> 1:28:38.313
- Because I've been
praying for you.

1:28:40.619 --> 1:28:45.537
[chuckles] I've been praying
for you your whole life.

1:28:46.321 --> 1:28:47.017
- [Brucie] What?

1:28:47.887 --> 1:28:50.325
[Ike chuckles]

1:29:03.468 --> 1:29:06.166
- I will always watch over you.

1:29:08.386 --> 1:29:09.866
[chuckles]

1:29:09.953 --> 1:29:13.478
I gave this to you on
the day you were born.

1:29:15.698 --> 1:29:18.918
- Hey, Brucie, is
everything all right?

1:29:21.617 --> 1:29:23.009
- Untold riches.

1:29:26.230 --> 1:29:27.187
Untold riches.

1:29:34.673 --> 1:29:35.631
- Hey, um...

1:29:39.504 --> 1:29:44.335
You think I could buy you a
cup of coffee or something?

1:29:44.422 --> 1:29:48.252
I have some things I'd
really like to tell you.

1:29:49.732 --> 1:29:52.822
- Boy, do I have a
story to tell you.

1:30:23.722 --> 1:30:25.115
- [Luc] Gabriel.

1:30:26.551 --> 1:30:27.334
- Lucifer!

1:30:29.336 --> 1:30:31.556
I have a message for
you, from the most high.

1:30:31.643 --> 1:30:33.645
You've been defeated.

1:30:33.732 --> 1:30:35.386
You no longer matter.

1:30:35.473 --> 1:30:37.997
[wind howls]

1:30:42.437 --> 1:30:44.700
[whooshes]

1:30:46.397 --> 1:30:48.443
[laughs]

1:30:58.235 --> 1:31:01.064
[upbeat rock music]

1:31:23.608 --> 1:31:26.655
♪ Look into the
night sky, baby ♪

1:31:26.742 --> 1:31:29.875
♪ Pick a shining star ♪

1:31:29.962 --> 1:31:32.704
♪ Make a wish that
may come true ♪

1:31:32.791 --> 1:31:36.360
♪ Believe in who you are ♪

1:31:36.447 --> 1:31:39.406
♪ Set your sights so very high ♪

1:31:39.494 --> 1:31:42.714
♪ There's nothing you can't do ♪

1:31:42.801 --> 1:31:45.282
♪ Be careful on what you wish ♪

1:31:45.369 --> 1:31:49.112
♪ Because wishes can come true ♪

1:31:49.199 --> 1:31:52.376
♪ So dream a dream,
wish a wish ♪

1:31:52.463 --> 1:31:55.597
♪ Close your eyes
and blow a kiss ♪

1:31:55.684 --> 1:31:58.817
♪ Follow your heart
and see it through ♪

1:31:58.904 --> 1:32:02.517
♪ Dreams and wishes come true ♪

1:32:14.790 --> 1:32:17.749
♪ Deep inside of you and I ♪

1:32:17.836 --> 1:32:20.796
♪ There lives another soul ♪

1:32:20.883 --> 1:32:24.321
♪ Who is very quiet
and very shy ♪

1:32:24.408 --> 1:32:27.324
♪ Unwilling to take control ♪

1:32:27.411 --> 1:32:30.545
♪ If we can just let
this soul appear ♪

1:32:30.632 --> 1:32:33.852
♪ And walk us
through this dream ♪

1:32:33.939 --> 1:32:36.638
♪ Then we can live
another life ♪

1:32:36.725 --> 1:32:40.337
♪ One that we have
never dreamed ♪

1:32:40.424 --> 1:32:43.470
♪ So dream a dream,
wish a wish ♪

1:32:43.558 --> 1:32:46.735
♪ Close your eyes
and blow a kiss ♪

1:32:46.822 --> 1:32:49.868
♪ Follow your heart
and see it through ♪

1:32:49.955 --> 1:32:53.698
♪ Dreams and wishes come true ♪
